    "name": "Dormy Inn Premium Shibuya Jingumae Hot Spring",
    "detail": "We stayed at this hotel at three separate occasions in March 2012 and the hotel was newly opened so everything was very fresh and clean. The rooms are stylish but a little small as is usual in Tokyo hotels. The spa, wich is included in the room price, was fantastic. It has a hot bath, showers and a sauna. We also tried the massage wich was very good. The staff was beyond accommodating and very nice. The location is only about 7 minutes walk from Harajuku JR Station and very close to a subway station. It sits between Harajuku and Shibuya so you can easily walk to Shibuya. We loved it and we will return next time in Tokyo. ",
